node.text: In case you missed it, Jeff Leatham went on his Instagram Live to talk all things #KKWxJEFF and answer your questions about the fragrance collection with @kimkardashian.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by KKW FRAGRANCE on August 12, 2021 tagging @kimkardashian. May be an image of 1 person and footwear.

node.text: Like it’s precious gemstone namesake, Emerald Diamond enchants the senses. Receive a free Trio Purse Spray with your next order of Emerald Diamond’s blooming white floral fragrance. Offer ends Sunday 8.15 at 11:59PM PT

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by KKW FRAGRANCE on August 11, 2021. May be a closeup.

node.text: Olive invites you closer to experience its magnetic scent. Tap to shop and wrap yourself in sleek white florals, jasmine, and vibrant solar amber.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by KKW FRAGRANCE on August 10, 2021.

node.text: Happy birthday @kyliejenner! To celebrate Kylie’s 24th birthday, we’re offering 24% off her signature KKW Fragrance collection — today only. Save on Pink Lips, Red Lips, Nude Lips, or the full bundle before tonight at 11:59PM PT.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by KKW FRAGRANCE on August 09, 2021.

node.text:
In an Olive and Amber daze. 

Tap to shop #KKWxKENDALL now✨

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by KKW FRAGRANCE on August 08, 2021 tagging @looksbyashvin. May be an image of fragrance.

node.text:
Body III and Olive, together in harmony.
Don't forget, we're throwing in a free trio purse spray with all Body III purchases. Ends TONIGHT at 11:59PM PT.

📸: @looksbyashvin

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by KKW FRAGRANCE on August 07, 2021 tagging @zacharyspencer. May be an image of saddle-stitched leather and text that says 'KKW EMERALD FRAGRANCE DIAMOND CRYSTAL KKWFRAGRANCE FRAGRANCE KKW KKWFRAGRANCE GARDENIA BODY'.

node.text:
There are many reasons to love Body I, Crystal Gardenia, and Emerald Diamond. Not only are they our best-selling scents, but they also come packaged together in the perfect size to throw in your purse. Now until Sunday 8.8 at 11:59PM PT, a free Trio Purse Spray will be included in all orders of Body III.

📸: @zacharyspencer

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by KKW FRAGRANCE on August 06, 2021 tagging @zacharyspencer. May be a closeup.

node.text:
Crafted from an alluring blend of floral, modern, and woody notes, each scent works in perfect harmony to create Body III’s versatile fragrance. Don't forget, we're throwing in a free trio purse spray with all Body III purchases before Sunday 8.8 at 11:59PM PT.

📸: @zacharyspencer

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by KKW FRAGRANCE on August 05, 2021 tagging @zacharyspencer.

node.text:
Now through Sunday, a free Trio Purse Spray will be included in all orders of Body III. Add Body III to cart, gift will be added automatically. Offer ends 8.8 at 11:59PM PT. Your gift with purchase awaits...

📸: @zacharyspencer

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by KKW FRAGRANCE on August 04, 2021.

node.text: Forego the labels of feminine and masculine. The dualistic combination of Olive’s scents strike just the right balance between bold and delicate, making it the perfect fragrance for everyone in your life.

node.text:
Night Iris is mysterious, alluring...and we're not just talking about the scent. Repurpose empty Night Iris into an elegant bud vase to display 🖤 Shop the #KKWxJeff fragrance at the link in our bio. 

📸: @beautybyrog

node.text: Happy #NationalSistersDay! Celebrate National Sisters Day with 20% off some of our most sentimental scents. For just a few more hours, head to the link in bio to save on all of @kimkardashian’s sister fragrance collabs. Ends tonight at 11:59PM PT.
